name: "The Next Train Will Be Approaching in...."
description: A photo I took on the Greenpoint Avenue station platform, a station that holds many memories of missing that last train and waiting for what felt like hours for the next one to arrive. There is no train in this image, it is not approaching, it is an illusion. Digitally manipulated in PS, layered with an image of an old neighborhood map of Greenpoint Brooklyn, also found ripped and weathered on the wall inside the station.
